            "title": "黑期夜期齊衝二萬七 重磅港股ADR全升阿里漲逾5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時16分升382點或1.44%，報26946點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報26983點，較香港上日現貨收市高374點或1.41%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣642.4元，較上日香港收市高19.39元或3.11%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣162.1元，較上日香港收市高7.77元或5.03%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣107元，較上日香港收市高2.04元或1.94%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣119.8元，較上日香港收市高2.89元或2.47%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣39.5元，較上日香港收市高0.72元1.86 %。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣126.8元，較上日香港收市高2.68元或2.16%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣85.1元，較上日香港收市高1.41元或1.69%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣433.5元，較上日香港收市高7.34元或1.72%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣69.5元，較上日香港收市高0.96元或1.4%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.8元，較上日香港收市高0.04元或0.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指期貨夜市收報26994點，升397點，較上日恒指收市26608點，高水386點。科指期貨夜市收報6005點，較上日科指收市高水142點；國指期貨夜市收報9365點，較上日國指收市高水145點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577533-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e9%bd%8a%e8%a1%9d%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%85%a8%e5%8d%87%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be5",
